{
  "_comment": "Sources for build-plugin-index.mjs. Add GitHub repos as 'owner/repo' under \"repos\", or whole users/orgs under \"users\" (every public repo is scanned). \"repoDirs\" is seeded from the existing catalog (repoDir = owner-repo joined by '-'; the script resolves the split via the GitHub API). \"searchQueries\" = repository search; \"codeSearchQueries\" = code search over the plugin annotations themselves (auth required; finds repos with no metadata and header-only MIT grants worldwide). Automatically discovered repos that ship the RPG Maker runtime (deployed games) are skipped. A plugin is included only with an explicit MIT grant: the repo's SPDX license, or an MIT declaration in the plugin header (for repos without a LICENSE file). Plugins containing @no-localize are skipped.",
